definitions.definition: Any of many elongated arthropods , of the class Diplopoda , with cylindrical bodies that have two pairs of legs for each one of their 20 to 100 or more body segments .

main_definition: Any of many elongated arthropods , of the class Diplopoda , with cylindrical bodies that have two pairs of legs for each one of their 20 to 100 or more body segments . [from 1601]
